Roy Redgrave https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roy_Redgrave 0 George Ellsworthy "Roy" Redgrave (26 April 1873 – 25 May 1922) was an English stage and silent film actor. Redgrave is considered to be the first member of the Redgrave acting dynasty. George_Ellsworthy_"_Roy_"_Redgrave ( 26_April_1873 – 25_May_1922 ) was an_English_stage and silent_film_actor .
